headline.main: Spain Public Debt Seen at 99.26 Percent of GDP End 2016-Treasury Source
headline.print_headline: Spain Public Debt Seen at 99.26 Percent of GDP End 2016-Treasury Source

lead_paragraph: Spanish public debt stood at 99.26 percent of gross domestic product (GDP) at the end of 2016 according to provisional data, a Treasury source said on Monday.
